docs.text: Welcome to the CoderDojo Twin Cities Mentoring Resources web site. The goal of this site is to provide resources for anyone that is mentoring students that would like to learn how to code. This site has shared resources and links to subject specific sub-sites. List of Subjects Scratch Python Robots Arduino App Inventor Unity Game Engine Web an User Experience (UX) Java Ruby
